WEBVTT

00:35.660 --> 00:37.490
<b>There he is! Get the guns ready!</b>

00:47.460 --> 00:48.460
<b>Kill him!</b>

01:08.350 --> 01:10.150
<b>Die, asshole!</b>

01:17.410 --> 01:18.450
<b>Damn it!</b>

01:41.850 --> 01:43.640
<b>Shit! Where is he?</b>

01:43.720 --> 01:44.970
<b>Where'd he go?</b>

01:45.060 --> 01:46.600
<b>Show yourself!</b>

01:46.680 --> 01:47.690
<b>You son of a bitch!</b>

01:47.770 --> 01:50.610
<b><i>There once was a legendary hit man.</i></b>

01:51.480 --> 01:53.110
<b><i>His name was…</i></b>

01:56.780 --> 01:59.410
<b><i>Taro Sakamoto.</i></b>

02:02.870 --> 02:07.410
<b><i>He was feared by every gangster,</i></b>

02:07.500 --> 02:11.380
<b><i>admired by every hit man.</i></b>

02:12.380 --> 02:14.300
<b><i>Until, one day…</i></b>

02:16.760 --> 02:18.510
<b>Hi! May I help you?</b>

02:21.850 --> 02:23.930
<b><i>He fell in love.</i></b>

02:25.060 --> 02:26.310
<b><i>He retired,</i></b>

02:27.390 --> 02:28.430
<b><i>got married,</i></b>

02:29.350 --> 02:30.690
<b><i>had a child,</i></b>

02:31.190 --> 02:32.060
<b><i>and…</i></b>

02:34.730 --> 02:37.940
<b><i>Sakamoto got fat.</i></b>

04:12.250 --> 04:15.080
<b>THE LEGENDARY HIT MAN</b>

04:15.170 --> 04:17.170
<b>SAKAMOTO'S</b>

04:17.250 --> 04:18.840
<b>This has to be it.</b>

04:19.670 --> 04:20.960
<b>I looked all over for you,</b>

04:21.460 --> 04:22.760
<b>Mr. Sakamoto.</b>

04:24.680 --> 04:25.970
<b>SAKAMOTO</b>

04:26.050 --> 04:27.890
<b>Hey Mister, watch this!</b>

04:28.470 --> 04:32.270
<b>If I can hit this target,
you have to give me a free juice box!</b>

04:32.350 --> 04:34.560
<b>Oh my, what are you doing?</b>

04:34.640 --> 04:37.400
<b>He's been coming a lot recently, huh?</b>

04:37.480 --> 04:38.360
<b>Yep.</b>

04:43.110 --> 04:45.360
<b>Oh, darn it!</b>

04:45.450 --> 04:46.280
<b>One more try!</b>

04:46.360 --> 04:49.080
<b>Mister, watch me get it this time!</b>

04:49.830 --> 04:50.660
<b>Oops!</b>

04:50.740 --> 04:52.660
<b>CALLIGRAPHY INK</b>

04:56.790 --> 04:58.500
<b>Uh-oh.</b>

04:59.170 --> 05:01.460
<b>What the hell! You little brat!</b>

05:01.550 --> 05:02.840
<b>Look at my white pants!</b>

05:02.920 --> 05:05.590
<b>-Oh, no! Honey, what should we do?
-How dare you!</b>

05:05.680 --> 05:07.720
<b>Let me go!</b>

05:15.180 --> 05:16.390
<b>You're dead!</b>

05:27.530 --> 05:29.370
<b>Creepy fat-ass!</b>

05:30.070 --> 05:33.700
<b>Thank you, Mister…</b>

05:33.790 --> 05:35.790
<b>There, there, don't cry.</b>

05:35.870 --> 05:37.710
<b>There, there!</b>

05:37.790 --> 05:38.710
<b>Brilliant move.</b>

05:40.290 --> 05:43.380
<b>A pen into the lower jaw,
straight through the carotid artery.</b>

05:44.340 --> 05:46.170
<b>I could see it.</b>

05:47.630 --> 05:50.090
<b>It's been too long, Mr. Sakamoto.</b>

05:51.010 --> 05:52.470
<b>It's me, Shin the Psychic.</b>

05:53.390 --> 05:54.680
<b>HIT MAN / PSYCHIC
SHIN</b>

06:00.060 --> 06:02.820
<b>Stop killing people in your mind!</b>

06:02.900 --> 06:04.280
<b>It's me, Shin!</b>

06:04.360 --> 06:06.440
<b>I used to work under you!</b>

06:09.030 --> 06:11.120
<b>So it was true, huh?</b>

06:11.200 --> 06:12.370
<b>You went straight</b>

06:12.450 --> 06:14.950
<b>-and started a mom-and-pop shop.
-Come on, let's go!</b>

06:15.040 --> 06:16.870
<b>SAKAMOTO'S</b>

06:16.950 --> 06:19.370
<b>Please come back, Mr. Sakamoto.</b>

06:19.460 --> 06:20.630
<b>You're too good.</b>

06:20.710 --> 06:22.920
<b>I mean, look at you now. That body!</b>

06:23.880 --> 06:25.550
<b><i>My days as a hit man are over.</i></b>

06:29.550 --> 06:33.550
<b><i>You used to be feared by every gangster.</i></b>

06:33.640 --> 06:35.930
<b><i>They called you "the legendary hit man."</i></b>

06:36.810 --> 06:39.440
<b>Why would you throw that all away?</b>

06:46.730 --> 06:47.610
<b><i>Delicious!</i></b>

06:48.190 --> 06:50.570
<b>You used to only eat field rations.</b>

06:51.200 --> 06:54.030
<b>Honestly, I can barely recognize you now.</b>

07:04.920 --> 07:07.090
<b><i>That… that speed!</i></b>

07:07.170 --> 07:09.670
<b><i>"Fat or not, I can kill you any day."</i></b>

07:09.760 --> 07:11.260
<b><i>Is that what he's telling me?</i></b>

07:12.930 --> 07:15.260
<b>Hi there, Mr. Sakamoto!</b>

07:15.350 --> 07:17.430
<b>Sorry to tear you away from your meal,</b>

07:17.520 --> 07:19.230
<b>but I've got a favor to ask.</b>

07:19.310 --> 07:21.350
<b><i>A favor from Mr. Sakamoto?</i></b>

07:22.350 --> 07:25.610
<b><i>Is he disguising as a civilian</i>
<i>to ask for a hit?</i></b>

07:27.570 --> 07:31.150
<b>This tree's gotten so tall,
I can't cut those branches.</b>

07:31.650 --> 07:33.490
<b>Can you get 'em, Mr. Sakamoto?</b>

07:34.820 --> 07:38.160
<b>Oh, looks great! You're amazing!</b>

07:38.870 --> 07:42.080
<b>Mr. Sakamoto,
my daughter won't eat her veggies.</b>

07:45.790 --> 07:46.960
<b>Yummy!</b>

07:47.800 --> 07:50.340
<b>We only have one ball to play with!</b>

07:55.180 --> 07:56.680
<b>Thank you!</b>

07:58.560 --> 08:00.640
<b>Are you the handyman for the whole town?!</b>

08:03.810 --> 08:04.940
<b>I get it now.</b>

08:05.020 --> 08:08.820
<b>You've done a good job
hiding your true identity.</b>

08:08.900 --> 08:11.070
<b>But I gotta say, Mr. Sakamoto,</b>

08:11.990 --> 08:13.820
<b>from where I'm standing,</b>

08:14.910 --> 08:17.070
<b>you just look ridiculous.</b>

08:17.740 --> 08:18.740
<b>I'll be back.</b>

08:21.290 --> 08:22.830
<b>You brat!</b>

08:27.840 --> 08:30.510
<b><i>It's been five years since I last saw him.</i></b>

08:31.170 --> 08:33.220
<b><i>He's let himself go in more ways than one.</i></b>

08:34.550 --> 08:35.470
<b><i>But…</i></b>

08:36.090 --> 08:39.600
<b><i>Damn, Mr. Sakamoto is awesome!</i></b>

08:39.680 --> 08:43.020
<b>Even with the extra weight,
he's still got that aura!</b>

08:43.100 --> 08:47.520
<b>If only! We could work! Together! Again!</b>

08:47.610 --> 08:48.690
<b>Don't look!</b>

08:50.480 --> 08:52.780
<b>BOSS</b>

08:54.030 --> 08:55.070
<b>Hello?</b>

08:55.150 --> 08:56.530
<b><i>Did you convince him?</i></b>

08:57.030 --> 08:57.910
<b>Well, no, but--</b>

08:57.990 --> 09:00.790
<b><i>So, you killed him, then?</i></b>

09:03.290 --> 09:04.290
<b>Boss.</b>

09:04.910 --> 09:07.710
<b>Come on, do we have to?</b>

09:07.790 --> 09:11.590
<b>Mr. Sakamoto's really fat now.
I don't think he'd cause any issues if--</b>

09:11.670 --> 09:12.880
<b>Shin.</b>

09:13.800 --> 09:18.140
<b>If someone disappears from the gang,
we make 'em disappear from the earth.</b>

09:18.800 --> 09:20.970
<b>That's the rule and Sakamoto broke it.</b>

09:21.470 --> 09:23.470
<b>We can't let him go.</b>

09:24.140 --> 09:25.890
<b>You know, Shin,</b>

09:26.520 --> 09:29.900
<b>if you can't get it done,
I can always send someone else!</b>

09:29.980 --> 09:32.570
<b>Stop complaining
or you'll be joining him in--</b>

09:33.610 --> 09:35.530
<b>Oh, shut up.</b>

09:38.240 --> 09:40.620
<b>Guess I have no choice…</b>

09:57.800 --> 09:59.050
<b>TWO DAYS' WORTH OF VITAMINS</b>

10:18.740 --> 10:21.530
<b><i>If I don't do it, someone else will.</i></b>

10:25.240 --> 10:26.950
<b><i>So if he's gonna die either way…</i></b>

10:32.130 --> 10:34.840
<b><i>I… should be the one to do it.</i></b>

10:36.590 --> 10:40.050
<b>Hey, what kind of poop
do you think this is?</b>

10:40.130 --> 10:42.800
<b>Ew! That's gross!</b>

10:44.310 --> 10:46.520
<b>Oh! You're the boy from yesterday.</b>

10:46.600 --> 10:47.980
<b>Shin, right?</b>

10:48.060 --> 10:49.850
<b>You're back already?</b>

10:51.270 --> 10:54.860
<b>Look what I found!
I think it's alien poop!</b>

10:55.690 --> 10:57.490
<b>Sorry, kiddos.</b>

10:59.820 --> 11:01.740
<b>It's time for war.</b>

11:16.050 --> 11:19.010
<b>ROBBERY SUSPECTS STILL AT LARGE!</b>

11:23.470 --> 11:25.350
<b>Hi again, Mr. Sakamoto.</b>

11:26.260 --> 11:30.100
<b>I'm probably going to leave town today,</b>

11:30.730 --> 11:32.980
<b>so I thought I'd come by to say…</b>

11:38.530 --> 11:39.530
<b>goodbye!</b>

11:51.160 --> 11:52.330
<b><i>A cough drop?</i></b>

12:01.510 --> 12:03.590
<b><i>Damn it, I can't read his mind.</i></b>

12:08.640 --> 12:09.680
<b><i>Where is he?</i></b>

12:10.560 --> 12:11.980
<b>SOOTHING COUGH DROPS</b>

12:27.740 --> 12:28.830
<b>CUSTARD CREAM PUFF</b>

12:28.910 --> 12:31.370
<b><i>Damn it! I gotta fix my stance and--</i></b>

12:40.380 --> 12:41.300
<b><i>Damn…</i></b>

12:48.180 --> 12:51.390
<b><i>What was I thinking…</i></b>

13:00.400 --> 13:03.320
<b>Dinner's almost ready!
Help me set the table.</b>

13:03.400 --> 13:04.450
<b>Okay!</b>

13:06.450 --> 13:08.490
<b>Hey, he's awake!</b>

13:08.570 --> 13:09.870
<b>Oh!</b>

13:09.950 --> 13:11.410
<b>Thank goodness.</b>

13:14.500 --> 13:15.710
<b>Where am I?</b>

13:16.330 --> 13:18.040
<b>The second floor above the shop.</b>

13:20.460 --> 13:22.710
<b>Why don't you join us for dinner?</b>

13:22.800 --> 13:23.630
<b>Huh?</b>

13:23.710 --> 13:25.970
<b>-Um…
-Do you want extra rice?</b>

13:26.050 --> 13:28.390
<b>Extra extra? Mega extra?</b>

13:29.640 --> 13:30.930
<b>A normal amount, please.</b>

13:32.060 --> 13:33.810
<b>-Let's eat!
-Let's eat!</b>

13:33.890 --> 13:36.730
<b><i>How did this happen?</i></b>

13:36.810 --> 13:38.100
<b><i>I tried to kill him…</i></b>

13:39.900 --> 13:41.360
<b><i>Wait, maybe this is poisoned!</i></b>

13:42.980 --> 13:45.190
<b><i>I've trained to withstand poison.</i>
<i>I'll be fine.</i></b>

13:51.990 --> 13:53.040
<b>So good…</b>

13:54.290 --> 13:55.790
<b>So warm!</b>

13:57.040 --> 13:59.420
<b>He's reacting just like you did back then.</b>

13:59.500 --> 14:01.290
<b>Same as Daddy!</b>

14:02.380 --> 14:03.340
<b><i>What is it?</i></b>

14:03.920 --> 14:05.300
<b><i>What is this feeling?</i></b>

14:05.880 --> 14:08.880
<b><i>I've never felt this way in</i>
<i>any of the jobs I've done.</i></b>

14:10.470 --> 14:11.550
<b><i>I get it now.</i></b>

14:12.970 --> 14:14.770
<b><i>Mr. Sakamoto…</i></b>

14:14.850 --> 14:18.390
<b><i>wants to protect these little moments</i>
<i>of everyday life.</i></b>

14:19.850 --> 14:21.020
<b><i>That's why he quit…</i></b>

14:25.230 --> 14:29.660
<b>SAKAMOTO'S</b>

14:30.700 --> 14:32.030
<b>Mr. Sakamoto,</b>

14:32.120 --> 14:33.120
<b>I…</b>

14:37.710 --> 14:39.080
<b>Thank you for dinner.</b>

14:43.250 --> 14:45.880
<b>THANK YOU! PLEASE COME AGAIN.
-SAKAMOTO'S</b>

14:50.300 --> 14:52.680
<b><i>I'm still no match</i></b>

14:52.760 --> 14:54.350
<b><i>for Mr. Sakamoto.</i></b>

15:04.650 --> 15:07.070
<b>What is it, Shin?</b>

15:10.490 --> 15:12.110
<b>What an embarrassment.</b>

15:12.200 --> 15:15.370
<b>You couldn't kill him, could you?</b>

15:16.700 --> 15:17.790
<b>Boss…</b>

15:17.870 --> 15:18.910
<b>What?</b>

15:19.000 --> 15:20.830
<b>Don't give me any excuses.</b>

15:20.920 --> 15:23.790
<b>Please let Mr. Sakamoto live!</b>

15:24.920 --> 15:27.630
<b>-How pathetic!
-What's wrong with you, Shin?</b>

15:28.630 --> 15:30.090
<b>Why?</b>

15:30.170 --> 15:32.180
<b>Why are you defending Sakamoto?</b>

15:32.260 --> 15:36.100
<b>He has people to go home to now.</b>

15:36.180 --> 15:39.520
<b>Sakamoto broke the rules of our world.</b>

15:39.600 --> 15:41.850
<b>He abandoned his responsibilities.</b>

15:41.940 --> 15:43.350
<b>So, we must kill him.</b>

15:44.150 --> 15:45.650
<b>Then hold me responsible.</b>

15:45.730 --> 15:47.320
<b>I'll die instead.</b>

15:48.110 --> 15:50.240
<b>So please, let Mr. Sakamoto go.</b>

15:51.070 --> 15:52.860
<b>Why are you doing this for him?</b>

15:54.240 --> 15:56.780
<b>I pointed my gun at someone I admired.</b>

15:57.700 --> 15:59.240
<b>This is my way of owning up.</b>

16:01.540 --> 16:03.000
<b>Fine.</b>

16:03.080 --> 16:06.250
<b>You die and I'll let Sakamoto live.</b>

16:08.000 --> 16:09.250
<b><i>Dumbass.</i></b>

16:09.340 --> 16:11.470
<b><i>As if I'd ever let that happen.</i></b>

16:11.550 --> 16:13.180
<b><i>Just die, you idiot.</i></b>

16:14.090 --> 16:15.430
<b>I heard that.</b>

16:17.010 --> 16:19.180
<b>I knew I couldn't expect much from you.</b>

16:19.260 --> 16:20.810
<b><i>Did he read my mind?</i></b>

16:21.680 --> 16:22.690
<b>Kill him!</b>

16:22.770 --> 16:23.980
<b><i>Bring it on.</i></b>

16:24.770 --> 16:27.020
<b>SAKAMOTO'S</b>

17:11.820 --> 17:13.530
<b><i>I'll blow his brains out!</i></b>

17:28.210 --> 17:30.250
<b><i>I can see everything from up here.</i></b>

17:34.050 --> 17:35.050
<b>Damn it!</b>

17:35.130 --> 17:37.430
<b>What are you doing? It's just one guy!</b>

17:37.510 --> 17:40.720
<b>It's like he knows what we're about to do.</b>

17:40.800 --> 17:42.970
<b>He's a psychic!</b>

17:43.060 --> 17:45.230
<b>If you get too close,
he'll read your mind.</b>

17:45.310 --> 17:47.100
<b>Keep your distance, surround him!</b>

17:58.660 --> 18:00.280
<b><i>This is my last mag.</i></b>

18:01.950 --> 18:03.620
<b><i>I gotta force my way out somehow.</i></b>

18:09.120 --> 18:10.000
<b><i>Damn it!</i></b>

18:20.050 --> 18:21.180
<b><i>I guess this is it…</i></b>

18:33.520 --> 18:35.030
<b>Mr. Sakamoto…</b>

18:35.110 --> 18:37.070
<b>Sakamoto?</b>

18:37.150 --> 18:38.030
<b>Kill him!</b>

18:39.030 --> 18:40.110
<b>Die!</b>

18:47.450 --> 18:48.460
<b>Son of a--</b>

18:55.250 --> 18:56.670
<b>Go to hell!</b>

19:07.390 --> 19:08.270
<b>Shit!</b>

19:12.520 --> 19:13.980
<b>Screw you!</b>

19:16.360 --> 19:18.990
<b>WASTE</b>

19:27.040 --> 19:29.410
<b><i>What… just happened?</i></b>

19:29.500 --> 19:31.000
<b>You're dead!</b>

19:35.250 --> 19:36.840
<b>Don't try to take him on alone.</b>

19:36.920 --> 19:38.260
<b>We'll shoot together.</b>

19:42.430 --> 19:43.550
<b>Now!</b>

19:53.770 --> 19:55.560
<b>You… piece of shit!</b>

19:57.820 --> 19:59.230
<b><i>This is insane.</i></b>

19:59.320 --> 20:00.190
<b><i>It's him.</i></b>

20:01.900 --> 20:03.610
<b><i>The legendary hit man,</i></b>

20:04.450 --> 20:05.870
<b><i>Taro Sakamoto!</i></b>

20:09.240 --> 20:11.620
<b>Mr. Sakamoto, how'd you know I was here?</b>

20:17.710 --> 20:19.880
<b>What? A bug?</b>

20:20.630 --> 20:23.050
<b><i>Did you plant this last night?</i></b>

20:23.130 --> 20:25.140
<b><i>Nothing gets past you, does it?</i></b>

20:26.390 --> 20:27.760
<b>Mr. Sakamoto,</b>

20:27.850 --> 20:29.390
<b>I actually meant what I said.</b>

20:29.970 --> 20:31.810
<b>No matter the outcome,</b>

20:32.350 --> 20:35.310
<b>I was gonna leave town toda--</b>

20:36.520 --> 20:37.400
<b>SHIN</b>

20:37.480 --> 20:38.940
<b>An apron?</b>

20:39.520 --> 20:41.240
<b>Eight hundred yen an hour.</b>

20:41.780 --> 20:43.700
<b>For overtime…</b>

20:45.660 --> 20:46.570
<b>I'll pay extra.</b>

20:46.660 --> 20:47.660
<b><i>What?</i></b>

20:55.870 --> 20:57.540
<b>SAKAMOTO'S</b>

20:57.630 --> 20:58.790
<b>Mr. Sakamoto,</b>

20:59.420 --> 21:02.130
<b>could you not eat ramen right next to me?</b>

21:03.800 --> 21:05.630
<b>This is a brand-new shirt.</b>

21:06.390 --> 21:09.050
<b>Plus, we're running out of ramen…</b>

21:09.140 --> 21:10.970
<b>We're home!</b>

21:11.060 --> 21:12.430
<b>Oh, my!</b>

21:12.520 --> 21:14.690
<b>Shin, the apron looks great on you.</b>

21:14.770 --> 21:16.020
<b>Oh, does it?</b>

21:16.100 --> 21:17.770
<b>Lookin' dapper!</b>

21:22.440 --> 21:24.190
<b>Here you go, ma'am.</b>

21:24.280 --> 21:27.110
<b>Oh, how'd you know?</b>

21:27.200 --> 21:29.200
<b>This is just what I was looking for!</b>

21:29.280 --> 21:30.530
<b>Thank you, sweetie.</b>

21:30.620 --> 21:32.540
<b>He really is psychic!</b>

21:32.620 --> 21:34.960
<b>Hey! Come play with me!</b>

21:35.040 --> 21:36.250
<b>After my shift's over.</b>

21:36.920 --> 21:37.830
<b>Come on!</b>

21:37.920 --> 21:40.130
<b>Is that even fun?</b>

21:40.210 --> 21:42.960
<b>Well, I don't really know yet,</b>

21:43.710 --> 21:46.380
<b>but it beats my last job for sure.</b>

21:46.470 --> 21:48.550
<b>What'd you do at your last job?</b>

21:48.640 --> 21:50.010
<b><i>Tell him and I'll kill you.</i></b>

21:51.470 --> 21:54.430
<b>Well, you could say I was a cleaner!</b>

21:54.520 --> 21:55.520
<b>In a sense.</b>

22:02.480 --> 22:03.940
<b>Hurry up!</b>

22:05.240 --> 22:06.700
<b>Welcome in!</b>

23:32.450 --> 23:37.450
<b>Subtitle translation by: Yuka Kristi</b>
